    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const cvContext = $node['📄 Structure CV Text'].json.cvText || '';\nconst job = $json;\nconst jt = (job.title || '').replace(/\"/g,'');\nconst co = (job.company || '').replace(/\"/g,'');\nconst lk = (job.link || job.fullLink || '').replace(/\"/g,'');\nconst lo = (job.location || '').replace(/\"/g,'');\nconst desc = (job.description || job.title || '').replace(/\"/g,'');\nconst pt = (job.postedTime || '').replace(/\"/g,'');\nconst ji = (job.jobId || '').replace(/\"/g,'');\n\nconst meta = JSON.stringify({title:jt,company:co,link:lk,location:lo,postedTime:pt,jobId:ji});\n\nconst prompt = `You are a professional recruitment matching consultant. Evaluate the match between the candidate's CV and the job posting.\n\n## Original Data (return as-is)\n__META__${meta}__META_END__\n\n${cvContext}\n\n### Job Info\n**职位**: ${jt}\n**公司**: ${co}\n**地点**: ${lo || '慕尼黑/巴伐利亚'}\n**描述**: ${desc || jt}\n\n### Scoring Criteria\n\n| 维度 | 分值范围 | 评分指引 |\n|------|---------|---------|\n| background_match | 0-10 | Domain/industry alignment：10=岗位行业与候选人CV专业领域完全吻合；6-9=相关或可转移领域；0=完全不相关 |\n| skills_overlap | 0-25 | Skills overlap: compare tech stack, tools, methodologies. More matches = higher score |\n| experience_relevance | 0-25 | Experience relevance: how well does the candidate's experience match the role requirements |\n| seniority | 0-10 | Seniority match: 10=perfect, 5=moderate, 0=not matching |\n| language_requirement | 0-10 | Language: 10=full match (German C1+English C1), 5=partial, 0=not matching |\n| location_match | 0-10 | Location: 10=Munich area, 8=Bavaria/Hybrid, 5=Germany/Remote, 0=abroad |\n\nTotal overall = background_match + skills_overlap + experience_relevance + seniority + language_requirement + location_match\n- Automotive industry: deduct 5 from background_match\n- Defense/Aerospace industry: deduct 10 from background_match (citizenship restriction)\n\n## Recommendation\n- overall >= 75 → \"Highly Match\"\n- overall >= 60 → \"Can Try\"\n- overall < 60 → \"Unfit\"\n\n## Output Format (strict JSON, no extra content)\n{\n  \"score\": { \"overall\": 82, \"background_match\": 8, \"skills_overlap\": 20, \"experience_relevance\": 22, \"seniority\": 8, \"language_requirement\": 8, \"location_match\": 10 },\n  \"recommendation\": \"Highly Match\",\n  \"industry\": \"Automotive\",\n  \"reason\": \"Brief match reason\",\n  \"_meta\": ${meta}\n}`;\n\nreturn [{ prompt: prompt }];"
      },
      "id": "d2eacb61-4673-4f3f-be67-4cac2af8f09f",
